I've spent four decades thinking about cooperative economics. Nine years building a platform. The last five months at ludicrous speed. I've filed 928 patent claims since November 26, 2025—many of them for innovations in modular hex systems that push what's possible.

**HexIsle is hydraulic hex terrain.** Water flows through modular hexagonal tiles. Real physics—gravity-powered waterfalls, rivers, cascades. No batteries, no pumps.

Your modularity expertise + our kinetic patents = terrain systems that move as seamlessly as they connect.

I'm not looking to absorb TerraTiles. I'm looking to amplify it.

**What you keep:** Your brand. Your designs. Your customers.

**What you gain:** Patent-protected technology. Manufacturing access. A cooperative network that expands your market.

The attached one-pager shows the numbers.

---

